    <item>
      <title>०५९ भारतकथनप्रतिज्ञा</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/01_Adiparva/06_aMshAvataraNaparva/059_bhAratakathanapratijnA/</link>
